<br>
I would / will love to have the epic.  I am very close to getting it, and will continue to try.  But the only thing epic about it now is the pet.  The item you hold is outdated stat wise for alot of people.<br>
<br>
A Warrior can go to ST, and get a weapon that increases his dps greatly.  Same with any meele class.  Well we are a combo of meele and nukes.  But our meele has not scaled up without direct intervention from VI in 2 Expansion.  So i would hope that people realize for the betterment of the class, the epic has to be surpased in damage, even if it is only against certain mobs or for certain zones.  <br>
