The epic quest was not meant to MQ'd.  You can but it wasn't maeant to be.  For those of us that did the vast majority of it the intended way.. It's a HUGE time sink. <br>
<br>
On another sub-topic, should the epic be epic forever, clearly not and here is why.<br>
<br>
First, comparing our epic to other classes is senseless, our epic is totally unlike other epics.  We all know that so lets not go there.  <br>
<br>
Second, don't forget that the epic was balanced (and reblanaced) based on soloing level 45 to 50 mobs and raiding mobs around 60.  In pop we will have to solo mobs 52 to 55+ I'd guess.  The epic is nice but it will not cut it solo against 55ish mobs.  Nor will it cut it when people start raiding level 75 mobs.<br>
<br>
Third, let be fair.  Some people did complete their epics in the low 50s.  It would be stupid of VI to allow anything from level 52 to scale all the way to level 65.  That would be just plain stupid.  The smart thing for VI to do is to have an a continuation of the epic.  Maybe the next epic would be level 55 and Hit for 100 or something.  <br>
<br>
Although the epic is a huge time sink, I think it is/was worth it.  Lets face though people, if the low end of the dark blue range ends up being 55 to 58, the old epic is going to have problems. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/ucyricusbloodbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cyricus Bloodbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1164<br> <font color=#333333>(10/22/02 2:08:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7455.topic&index=29>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://520013139003-001.bei.t-online.de/IWD_Human_Male_Wizard3.gif height=58 width=36></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Lets think about this</span><hr size=1> I find it pretty rude to hijack someone´s PoP pet thread with some senseless Epic vs other pet discussion we only had 5685877687796 times on this board.<br>
